---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Tooltails.com" description="Terms of Service for Tooltails.com. By using our age calculators and date tools, you agree to these terms.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-neutral">
      <p class="text-lg text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Welcome to Tooltails.com. By accessing or using our utility tools, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Use of Service</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our age and date calculation tools are provided for general informational purposes only. While we strive for maximum precision and accuracy, we cannot guarantee that the results will be 100% error-free in all edge cases or historical calendar shifts.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Your privacy is important to us. As stated in our Privacy Policy, all calculations are performed locally in your browser. We do not transmit or store your personal dates of birth on our servers.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        The service is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without any warranties of any kind. We do not accept liability for any decisions made based on the calculations provided by this website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Terms of Service - Tooltails.com",
    "description": "Terms of Service for Tooltails.com.",
    "url": Astro.url.origin + "/terms",
    "mainEntityOfPage": {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "@id": Astro.url.origin + "/terms"
    }
  })} />
</Layout>
